{
  "stem": "1343.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had no floor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was dirt, and it was in the springtime, so it was full with mud and water and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The windows had the frames, but no glass in it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We arrived at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They herded us into the barracks so tight that we could not sit down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were standing only.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In Mauthausen, you know, the sonderkommando was the group who operated the crematorias.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were better fed, [BACKGROUND NOISE] but every month or six weeks, they were all thrown into the ovens and were killed, and a new group.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this very last group, they had no time to kill, so they came with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And these kids were-- these were young, young Polish kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish Polish kids.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the group that I was in were several with us, and they were-- they had the [NON-ENGLISH], the strength, that they climbed up into the crossbeams and, with their belts, they tied themselves.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were the only ones who were stretched out, comfortable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the middle of the night, people were falling at each other, because they couldn't stand anymore, and there was a big tumult.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Germans yelled in, quiet!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't help.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave down a volley.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A gunshot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they killed a bunch of people, naturally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they shot one of the kids above my head.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That night, all night long, the blood was dripping on my-- either my head or my shoulder or wherever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When the light came, my uncle looked at me, and I was covered with blood, so they thought that they shot me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they started to strip me to see where the blood is coming from, but it was not.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
